clearBit(uint256,uint8).notice: Clears the bit at a given index (sets it to 0).

countSetBits(uint256).notice: Counts the number of bits set to 1 in the given number.

isBitSet(uint256,uint8).notice: Checks if the bit at a given index is set (1) in the number.

setBit(uint256,uint8).notice: Sets the bit at a given index to 1.

toggleBit(uint256,uint8).notice: Toggles the bit at a given index.

userdoc.notice: A contract demonstrating various bitwise operations on a uint256 value.
